<h1 id="overlay-title">Miss Trunchbull</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Miss Trunchbull is the dean of Matilda's school, her cruelty so needlessly over the top that the parents wouldn't believe it and don't.	</p>
